Title : 2014 Tunis Open – Singles
Text : {{context|date=December 2015}}
{{TennisEvents|2014|Tunis Open|
| champ = {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Simone Bolelli]]
| runner = {{flagicon|GER}} [[Julian Reister]]
| score  = 6–4, 6–2
| type = men
| after_year = 2018
}}

{{main|2014 Tunis Open}}

[[Adrian Ungur]] was the defending champion, but lost in the quarterfinals to [[Mate Delić]].

[[Simone Bolelli]] won the title, defeating [[Julian Reister]] in the final, 6–4, 6–2.

